{"tid":237242,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"好驚達哥有一日會唔再做直播","createTime":"2017-05-10T08:56:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-10T11:26:35.000Z","uid":7514,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b963484d453db8eba42d542467d9532c85450b27","tid":237242,"uid":7514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T08:56:04.000Z","msg":"我嘅生活差不多有一半時間都係同緊達哥一齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n會down定達仔打fifa讀有趣新聞坐車個陣聽<br />\n痾屎個陣會睇tatstory MUV<br />\n溫書溫到攰又會睇番佢以d打機片<br />\n2130會準時睇直播<br />\n訓教又會聽住佢以前打Fifa 個d有趣新聞<br />\n睇哂近期個d又會睇番佢以前個d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nJEFF都已經30歲 點都會結婚生仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔會再有咁多時間直播<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n總有一日會唔做 <br />\n我嘅生活就會好似無左一忽咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n達仔如果你有一日打算唔再做<br />\n希望你個排做得差d 令到你d fans 唔再想睇<br />\n咁樣做 起碼大家都唔會唔捨得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n達仔 我愛你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n <br />\nP.S 你係鏡頭面前真係好生硬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n都係直播個陣玩得開心d"},{"pid":"3c5bba1e22ee4bd65b51e93689164dac1912b312","tid":237242,"uid":45520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T08:57:42.000Z","msg":"苦戀注定難"},{"pid":"3c86021948916e47b5becbc8664786a9d3246851","tid":237242,"uid":11856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T08:58:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/10/165836_74e415df6b88b54a129b89a0cdecc527.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F10%2F165836_74e415df6b88b54a129b89a0cdecc527.jpg&h=11e1d837&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<